                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "27": {
                          "id": "27",
                          "speaker": "Halsin",
                          "text": "But I didn't bring you here to witness an old druid's grandstanding. You have a part to play in this - and I trust you will play it well.",
