                                                      "id": "24",
                                                      "speaker": "Halsin",
                                                      "text": "It's ready. I'll return with Thaniel as soon as possible. Stay close to the portal - buy me what time you can.",
                                                      "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Halsin looks up at the portal he's conjured, before speaking to the player. He then steps through the portal.\rNodeContext: Thaniel rhymes with Daniel. Urgent, addressed to the player.",
